<p>So â€¦ Iâ€™ve been buying American stocks. This is my personal account Iâ€™m talking about, in which I previously owned nothing but United States government bonds. (This description leaves aside my Berkshire Hathaway holdings, which are all committed to philanthropy.) If prices keep looking attractive, my non-Berkshire net worth will soon be 100 percent in United States equities.</p>

